file.name: address.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Address API
  license:
    name: Microsoft
paths:
  '/address/validate':
    post:
      summary: Validate Address
      operationId: validate_address
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/addressValidateRequest'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/addressValidateResponse'
components:
  schemas:
    addressValidateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        address:
          type: string
          example: "One Microsoft Way, Redmond, WA 98052, United States"
    addressValidateResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        valid:
          type: boolean
          example: true
